## **Connecting & Interacting**

- **SQL*Plus login:**
    

`sqlplus scott/tiger@<IP>/XE sqlplus scott/tiger@<IP>/XE as sysdba`

- **Basic enumeration:**
    

`-- List all tables select table_name from all_tables;  -- Check user privileges select * from user_role_privs;  -- Extract password hashes select name, password from sys.user$;`

